contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionarypar|ooo}} '''OOO''' may refer to: * OOO also means "Out of Office" * [[OpenOffice.org]], an office application suite * [[Out-of-order execution]], a paradigm in microprocessors * [[Limited liability company]] (Russian: Общество с ограниченной ответственностью, [[Romanization of Russian|traslit.]] ''Obshchestvo s Ogranichennoy Otvetstvennostyu''), a legal form of business company in Russia and other countries * ''[[Kamen Rider OOO]]'', a 2010-2011 tokusatsu series * The Land of Ooo, the setting of ''[[Adventure Time]]'' * OOO, the artistic identity of American musician and composer Nicholas Christos Raftis III, whose recordings have been released by [[Planet Mu]] and others * [[OOO gauge]], an old UK model railway scale * [[Object-oriented ontology]], a metaphysical theory '''O-O-O''' may refer to: * Long (or queenside) [[castling (chess)]], in Portable Game Notation ==See also== * [[000 emergency]], the primary national emergency number in Australia * [[One on One (disambiguation)]] * [[Out of Order (disambiguation)]] * [[Three Rings Design]], an online game developer * O00, the [[Alturas Municipal Airport]] * [[Order of operations]] {{disambiguation}}
